<expan>Turn<ex>er</ex></expan> von Styrn, sein armman, fürbraht und geklagt
                        hab, daz er gen euch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> sey
                                <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, darümb er
                            <expan>unsich<ex>er</ex></expan> vor ew sey und des er doch
                                <expan>unschuld<ex>ig</ex></expan> sey.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir des
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> armman sichert auf
                                <expan>fr<ex>euntlich</ex></expan> reht, des der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> von <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt gern <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wil, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des ermant wirdt. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan><ex>con</ex>cep<ex>cionis</ex></expan>
<expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ie</expan>. </ab>
